author: stsp
msg: On the 1.6.x-r38000 branch:
Merge r39000, r39002, r39007, and r39008 from trunk, all of which merged
without conflicts.
merge_test 133, merge_replace_causes_tree_conflict, now passes on this branch.
It doesn't use the new fancy "replaced" reasons that trunk has, however, and
reports "deleted" instead. Good enough for a backport though.

author: stsp
msg: On the 1.6.x-r38000 branch:
Merge r38907 from trunk, resolving conflicts.
Omit unnecessary edits to update_tests.py. Use svn_wc_conflict_reason_deleted
instead of svn_wc_conflict_reason_replaced (which only exists in trunk),
and explicitly query the entry's schedule to find out whether a victim is
scheduled for replacement.
